Subject: [PATCH] ASoC: SOF: topology: remove redundant code
Mime-version: 1.0
Content-type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-transfer-encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: fb763299bd8e075f1e9fb0a1cd296b0400fe8442
